PayablesJobErrorResult is a BusinessClass
	owned by ap
	prefix is PJER
	Ontology
		symbolic key is PayablesJobErrorResult
		
    Patterns
        disable AuditIndex
        disable Auditing
        disable EffectiveDated

	Persistent Fields
		PayablesCompany
		PayablesInvoice
		PayablesInvoicePayment
            delete ignored
		CashManagementGroup
		CashCode
		CashLedgerPayment
            delete ignored
		BankTransactionCode
		ErrorMessage						is Alpha size 200
		ErrorNumber							is a CashRequirementsErrorNumber
				
	Field Rules

	Conditions
		IsPayablesPayment
			when (PayablesInvoicePayment entered)

		IsCashLedgerPayment
			when (CashLedgerPayment entered)

		IsAlert
			when (ErrorNumber != CashRequirementsErrorNumber.VendorBankError)

	Actions
		Create is a Create Action
			restricted

		Update is an Update Action
			restricted

		Purge is a Purge Action
			restricted

		PurgePayablesJobErrorResults is a Set Action
			default label is untranslatable
			restricted
			Parameters
				PrmVendorGroup				is a VendorGroup
				PrmPayGroup					is a PayGroup
				PrmProcessGroup				is a PayablesProcessGroup
			Instance Selection
				where (VendorGroup							= PrmVendorGroup
				and    PayablesJobResult.PayGroup			= PrmPayGroup
				and    PayablesJobResult.ProcessGroup		= PrmProcessGroup)
			Action Rules
				Instance Rules
					invoke Purge
